        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2019-07-04 15:24:06.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nFrom code perspective looks fine, but from a arch design perspective, TLS/SSL termination should be handled outside of the business application (CDS-UI). i.e. no coupling of CDS-UI logic with managing keys & certs. Bc certs can expire and this is a self-signed cert",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "64c0576aaeb3a26313157efd15addb0627883490",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 4939,
          "name": "Nirvan Ramjuttun",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "nirvan.ramjuttun@amdocs.com",
          "username": "nirvan.ramjuttun"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2019-07-04 15:26:20.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nCouple of approaches for TLS termination: \n- API Gateway\n- side-car containers (per-host or per-container)  e.g ISTIO with Envoy\n- AAF ?",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "55f6186df992cf5e2ec2ea3ef54dd6f5a6aa44cc",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 5014,
          "name": "Xuefeng Xie",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "henry.xie@ericsson.com",
          "username": "eeginux"
        },
        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2019-07-04 15:54:55.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Patch Set 1:\n> \n> Couple of approaches for TLS termination: \n> - API Gateway\n> - side-car containers (per-host or per-container)  e.g ISTIO with Envoy\n> - AAF ?\nHi Nirvan, Thank you for the response and suggestion!\n\nI should submit this one as patch, the intention is to seek option and suggestion about the jira. \n\nAs told the AAF integration will happen in Frankfurt and AAF would provide the RBAC like for services. So for El alto release, is it ok to couple the cert management with CDS-UI and which cert should be used? Or it's better to try other approach, API gateway, side-car containers?",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "dbb4d8d6821b6b7cad44f6f0c42732fe5ddd6d52",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 87,
          "name": "Dan Timoney",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "dtimoney@att.com",
          "username": "djtimoney"
