        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2019-07-08 15:13:08.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review+2\n\nThis is okay for now, but probably need to use AAF issued certs to satisfy ONAP security standards. That can be a separate commit, though",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
